Lesson 5: Model Diagnostics

In Lesson 5, we will continue to introduce the modeling capabilities of the RsNLME package and demonstrate how to easily generate ggplot2 based model diagnostics plots using the Certara.Xpose.NLME and xpose packages. Finally, we will explore additional plot customization options using ggplot2 commands.




Webinar Overview

In the webinar we will cover the following topics:

  • Creating a data object (xpose_data) in R from RsNLME model output
  • Exploring model diagnostics with xpose and Certara.Xpose.NLME plot commands
  • Extending and customizing model diagnostics with ggplot2
